{"tid":1322913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無業男涉向警署投擲汽油彈 向官稱擁有美聯儲局儲備","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:00:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c2cc456b99d3597155cf0c1e2b6a60d406f5513c","tid":1322913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"涉嫌上月7日向灣仔警察總部外一輛警車及跑馬地警署外牆投擲汽油彈的25歲無業青年，在東區裁判法院再提訊。他被控兩項縱火罪，暫時毋須答辯，他第4次申請保釋被拒，須還押荔枝角收押所。被告莊鑫淼在庭上向裁判官表示，美國聯儲局的儲備由他擁有，又指20國峰會領袖可以替他做擔保，又問裁判官是否認識他。裁判官沒有回應被告的問題。<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-16 13:21:43"},{"pid":"6b2ee2a225ec16a3713ec18ca1e834e2d1650444","tid":1322913,"uid":38358,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想扮傻入青山"},{"pid":"53101f1bd22530bbe54b055d6ee95fc20cb5565b","tid":1322913,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"上次有單扮傻，但係無用"},{"pid":"8ed5ca2f81776c6b9ae834ed558a6f6f9ad58f88","tid":1322913,"uid":246586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"外國勢力出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34829e6f7190f77390a32a214b30dd385518837","tid":1322913,"uid":144492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"係咪想入落示威者度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e579cd90b635155faee4a09d7421699c3a00431","tid":1322913,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53101f1bd22530bbe54b055d6ee95fc20cb5565b","tid":1322913,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"上次有單扮傻，但係無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"條友25歲搞咩鳩"},{"pid":"a7860cecafe0c82c5715306005961de8019173ed","tid":1322913,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:48:23.000Z","msg":